    <p>This is the part most fans haven't fully worked out yet. The 48-team format creates a <strong>three-tier qualification system</strong> for the knockout stage.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>The <strong>top 2 finishers</strong> from each of the 12 groups advance automatically.</li>
      <li>That creates <strong>24 automatic qualifiers</strong> (12 group winners + 12 runners-up).</li>
